	<p><strong>Nelson WA Maths for the Australian Curriculum</strong>&nbsp;retains all of the features which made the original series so popular in Western Australia plus incorporates features designed specifically to cover the achievement standards, general capabilities and proficiency strands of the Australian Curriculum.&nbsp; Maintaining its coverage of years 7 &ndash; 10 Mathematics, this series continues to engage students with innovative Mathematics teaching for the Australian Curriculum. Components to accompany the student book, both printed and digital, are also available to teachers.</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #1f497d;">NelsonNet and the interactive NelsonNetBook&nbsp;</span><br />
<br />
</strong>Our Australian Curriculum titles are supported by a wide range of student and teacher resources, available on the NelsonNet password protected website. NelsonNet is also your portal to access the NelsonNetBook version of our student books. These web-based eBooks are compatible with iPads and interactive whiteboards. They are ideal as a supplement for the printed book or as a standalone option for schools seeking a digital-only resource solution. Trial the NelsonNetBook on the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.nelsonnet.com.au/" target="_blank">NelsonNet</a>&nbsp;website.&nbsp;</p>
